  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Brightshade Husk</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br><span class=\"box headnote\"><i>This content is available only after activating the</i> <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Rift\" title=\"Lunar Rift\"><img alt=\"Map Icon Lunar Rift.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Map_Icon_Lunar_Rift.png/28px-Map_Icon_Lunar_Rift.png?34c0a1\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Rift\" title=\"Lunar Rift\">Lunar Rift</a></i></span><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>The <b>Brightshade Husk</b> is a resource exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>, introduced in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/From_Beyond\" title=\"From Beyond\">From Beyond</a></i>. It can only be obtained by killing <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Deadly_Brightshade\" title=\"Deadly Brightshade\">Deadly Brightshades</a>. \n</p><p>Brightshade Husks can be used alongside <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance\" title=\"Pure Brilliance\">Pure Brilliance</a> to craft tools, armor, and weaponry at a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy\" title=\"Brightsmithy\">Brightsmithy</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightshade_Husk\" title=\"Brightshade Husk\"><img alt=\"Brightshade Husk.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Brightshade_Husk.png?7542e5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance\" title=\"Pure Brilliance\"><img alt=\"Pure Brilliance.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pure_Brilliance.png?102a2c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy\" title=\"Brightsmithy\"><img alt=\"Brightsmithy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Brightsmithy.png/42px-Brightsmithy.png?98c232\" width=\"42\" height=\"57\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightshade_Armor\" title=\"Brightshade Armor\"><img alt=\"Brightshade Armor.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Brightshade_Armor.png?4834b4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightshade_Husk\" title=\"Brightshade Husk\"><img alt=\"Brightshade Husk.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Brightshade_Husk.png?7542e5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance\" title=\"Pure Brilliance\"><img alt=\"Pure Brilliance.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pure_Brilliance.png?102a2c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy\" title=\"Brightsmithy\"><img alt=\"Brightsmithy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Brightsmithy.png/42px-Brightsmithy.png?98c232\" width=\"42\" height=\"57\"></a></td><