.png?e83114\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance\" title=\"Pure Brilliance\"><img alt=\"Pure Brilliance.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pure_Brilliance.png?102a2c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Rock\" title=\"Moon Rock\"><img alt=\"Moon Rock.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moon_Rock.png?189e68\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy\" title=\"Brightsmithy\"><img alt=\"Brightsmithy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Brightsmithy.png/42px-Brightsmithy.png?98c232\" width=\"42\" height=\"57\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Howlitzer\" title=\"Howlitzer\"><img alt=\"Howlitzer.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Howlitzer.png?17bee2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightshade_Husk\" title=\"Brightshade Husk\"><img alt=\"Brightshade Husk.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Brightshade_Husk.png?7542e5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy\" title=\"Brightsmithy\"><img alt=\"Brightsmithy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Brightsmithy.png/42px-Brightsmithy.png?98c232\" width=\"42\" height=\"57\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightshade_Husk_Rounds\" title=\"Brightshade Husk Rounds\"><img alt=\"Brightshade Husk Rounds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Brightshade_Husk_Rounds.png?831a8a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>20</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Walter\" title=\"Walter\"><img alt=\"Walter Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Walter_Portrait.png/64px-Walter_Portrait.png?4ca0a0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td><td class=\"dark-invert\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Slinger\" title=\"Lunar Slinger\"><img alt=\"Lunar Slinger.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lunar_Slinger.png?d83267\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Brightshade Husks were introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/From_Beyond#Taking_Root\" title=\"From Beyond\">Taking Root</a></i> update.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
