  "wikitext": "{{Object Infobox\n|image = Brightshade_Husk_Dropped.png\n|icon = Brightshade_Husk.png\n|droppedBy={{pic|30|Deadly Brightshade}}\n|stack=20\n|spawnCode=\"lunarplant_husk\"}}\n{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}{{Rift Content|Lunar Rift}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = It's incredibly tough. I could use this!\n|willow = Can I burn it now?\n|wolfgang = Ah. Is not haunted anymore.\n|wendy = It can't hurt anyone anymore.\n|wx78 = IT WAS OF NO USE TO ME ALIVE\n|wickerbottom = An extremely resilient material. I should make use of it.\n|woodie = That could be good for somethin'.\n|maxwell = The blasted thing is finally dead.\n|wigfrid = It hath a formidible hide, for a non-meat.\n|webber = That was one mean plant. We're glad it's gone!\n|winona = That's tough stuff!\n|warly = Ah, raw ingredients!\n|wormwood = Sorry\n|wortox = Unoccupied.\n|wurt = Hee-hee, it dead!\n|walter = If you kill a ghost plant, do you get... a double ghost?\n|wanda = What an interesting material, I should make use of it.\n|choose = walter\n}}\n\nThe '''Brightshade Husk''' is a resource exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'', introduced in ''[[From Beyond]]''. It can only be obtained by killing [[Deadly Brightshade]]s. \n\nBrightshade Husks can be used alongside [[Pure Brilliance]] to craft tools, armor, and weaponry at a [[Brightsmithy]].\n\n== {{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Brightshade Husk\n|count1=4\n|item2=Pure Brilliance\n|count2=4\n|result=Brightshade Armor\n|tool=Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Brightshade Husk\n|count1=2\n|item2=Pure Brilliance\n|count2=4\n|result=Brightshade Helm\n|tool=Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Brightshade Husk\n|count1=4\n|item2=Pure Brilliance\n|count2=4\n|result=Brightshade Bomb\n|tool=Brightsmithy\n|item3=Infused Moon Shard\n|count3=1\n|resultcount=6}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Brightshade Husk\n|count1=6\n|item2=Pure Brilliance\n|count2=3\n|result=Brightshade Staff\n|tool=Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Brightshade Husk\n|count1=3\n|item2=Pure Brilliance\n|count2=4\n|result=Brightshade Sword\n|tool=Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Brightshade Husk\n|count1=2\n|item2=Pure Brilliance\n|count2=1\n|result=Brightshade Smasher\n|tool=Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Brightshade Husk\n|count1=2\n|item2=Pure Brilliance\n|count2=1\n|result=Brightshade Shoevel\n|tool=Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Brightshade Husk\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Pure Brilliance\n|count2 = 1\n|result = Brightshade Repair Kit\n|tool = Brightsmithy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|tool = Brightsmithy\n|item2 = Spark Ark\n|item1 = Brightshade Husk\n|count1 = 3\n|item3= Pure Brilliance\n|count3= 3\n|item4 = Moon Rock\n|count4 = 3\n|result= Howlitzer\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Brightshade Husk\n|count1 = 1\n|tool = Brightsmithy\n|result = Brightshade Husk Rounds\n|resultcount = 20\n|character = Walter\n|skill = Lunar Slinger\n}}\n== {{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* Brightshade Husks were introduced in the ''[[From Beyond#Taking Root|Taking Root]]'' update.\n\n{{Resources}}\n[[Category:From Beyond]]\n[[vi:Brightshade Husk]]\n[[zh:亮茄外壳]]"
}
